{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/2021/08/ss-converter","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b42d85c8-3c69-5174-b88b-47c2137ed2c6","html":"<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">1. 前言</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">2. 安装及使用</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"1-前言\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"1 前言 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 前言</h2>\n<p>有点不记得当时为啥要使用这个转换工具了，应该是最早的<code class=\"language-text\">ClashX</code>不支持<code class=\"language-text\">ShadowSocks</code>协议导致我不得不使用工具来进行转换。不过我今天写这篇文章的时候看了下Clash的文档，貌似支持列表里已经有ShadowSocks了，不过因为我还没实际测试过，所以这个结论先保留下。</p>\n<p>总之，之前因为Clash的支持原因，需要使用第三方工具将SS的订阅转换成Clash支持的格式然后Clash才能正常更新SS的订阅。具体就要使用到<a href=\"https://github.com/tindy2013/subconverter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">tindy2013/subconverter</a>这个工具。因为之前找了好几次，所以这次留篇笔记来记录下，方便后续查找。</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-安装及使用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"2 安装及使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 安装及使用</h2>\n<p><strong>安装</strong></p>\n<p>参照这篇指引来安装docker container：<a href=\"https://github.com/tindy2013/subconverter/blob/master/README-docker.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">subconverter-docker</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ docker run -d --restart<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>always -p <span class=\"token number\">25500</span>:25500 tindy2013/subconverter:latest</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>使用</strong></p>\n<p>在Clash中输入下面的链接，来替代你自己机场的SS订阅链接：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">http://127.0.0.1:25500/sub?target<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>clash<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">url</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>replace_this_with_your_ss_subscription_link<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">config</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>%CONFIG%</code></pre></div>\n<p>最后的<code class=\"language-text\">config</code>那块是可选的，我基本上不配置。对应的文档在：<a href=\"https://github.com/tindy2013/subconverter#advanced-usage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Advanced Usage</a>。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>EOF</p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2021/08/ss-converter","tagSlugs":["/tag/shadow-socks/","/tag/clash/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-08-17T02:02:22.000Z","description":"如何在ClashX中使用SS订阅","tags":["ShadowSocks","Clash"],"title":"SS订阅转Clash","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/7e722e026a41a08a8f9a1cc76782dd27/default-social-image.jpg"}}},"allFile":{"totalCount":0,"nodes":[]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2021/08/ss-converter","gallery":"media/posts/2021/08/ss-converter/gallery"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}